an be very boring most of the time and I want to spend time with you as much as possible. <br><br>::After that, Persephone slowly leans in, holds his shoulders, tilts herhead upwards and kisses him deeply and passionately. Then, then her eyes still closed, she leans in and whispers in his ear:: And I want you to make love to me tonight like you never have before <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uixlordhadesxi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IX Lord Hades XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 174<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(3/17/02 2:25:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=242.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> An offer he cannot refuse...</span><hr size=1> ::Hades looks deep into Persephone's eyes, as if examinging her soul.  He then smiled slightly and whispered into her ear::<br><br>&quot;Of course...&quot;<br><br>::He then took her by the hand and started walking to his bedchambers.  Her hand in his::<br><br>&quot;And at dawn I shall escort you back to your mother...&quot;<br><br>::He hated the fact that she had to return for 6 months out of the year back to the upperworld, but it is somethign he learned to accept::<br><br>::With that he walked into the bedchamber with her and closed the door behind them::<br><br>----Let your imagination work from here on out----- <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/upersephoneqofu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PersephoneQofU</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 126<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(3/17/02 3:55:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?t